    <item>
      <title>叛国罪调查后韩国总统面临何种未来？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korea-can-president-yoon-be-arrested-investigated-for-treason</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈在弹劾投票中幸存下来，但继续执政并不能使他在实施戒严的灾难性尝试后免受调查。检察官和警方已对他的叛国罪指控展开调查。法律程序可能会拖延数月甚至数年，如果被判有罪，他可能会面临终身监禁或——尽管可能性不大——死刑。虽然韩国已经判处前总统叛国罪，并弹劾了另外两名总统]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korea-can-president-yoon-be-arrested-investigated-for-treason</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:40:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲与特朗普在打击大型科技公司问题上发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/europe-on-collision-course-with-trump-on-big-tech-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟多年来对一些美国最大公司的打压将迫使当选总统唐纳德·特朗普决定哪个更令他困扰：欧洲还是科技巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/europe-on-collision-course-with-trump-on-big-tech-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘密 Facebook 网络被发现针对罗马尼亚选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/covert-facebook-network-found-to-be-targeting-romanian-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[报告显示，在罗马尼亚大选前夕，Meta Platforms Inc. 允许一个 Facebook 页面网络发布超过 4,100 条政治广告，攻击罗马尼亚支持欧盟的总统候选人埃琳娜·拉斯科尼 (Elena Lasconi)，并宣传包括卡林·乔治斯库 (Calin Georgescu) 在内的极右翼人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/covert-facebook-network-found-to-be-targeting-romanian-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国警方考虑对尹永哲实施海外旅行禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korean-police-consider-overseas-travel-ban-on-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国警方表示，他们正在考虑是否对总统尹锡烈实施海外旅行禁令，目前他们正参与调查这位因短暂宣布戒严而陷入困境的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korean-police-consider-overseas-travel-ban-on-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 04:55:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰将为国有 Kiwibank 注资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/new-zealand-to-pursue-capital-injection-for-state-owned-kiwibank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府将向国有银行 Kiwibank 注资高达 5 亿新西兰元（2.9 亿美元），以增强由四家澳大利亚银行主导的银行业的竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/new-zealand-to-pursue-capital-injection-for-state-owned-kiwibank</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 04:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方称澳大利亚犹太教堂火灾“可能”是恐怖袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/australia-synagogue-fire-likely-a-terrorist-attack-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚执法机构已将南部城市墨尔本一座犹太教堂发生的疑似纵火袭击事件升级为“可能的”恐怖事件，并升级了对该事件的调查，促使以色列总理直接谴责堪培拉政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/australia-synagogue-fire-likely-a-terrorist-attack-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 03:29:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国工会威胁罢工，要求罢免尹永哲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korea-unions-threaten-to-strike-in-push-to-remove-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表韩国一些最大公司工人的工会威胁要罢工，要求总统尹锡烈辞职。上周末，尹锡烈险些被弹劾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korea-unions-threaten-to-strike-in-push-to-remove-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 02:56:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚签署第二份太平洋安全协议对中国造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/australia-inks-second-pacific-security-deal-in-blow-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚与太平洋国家瑙鲁签署了一项条约，赋予堪培拉对安全和基础设施合作伙伴的否决权，这对中国扩大在该地区战略存在的努力又一次打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/australia-inks-second-pacific-security-deal-in-blow-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 02:13:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
